summary: This mod adds some plants around Breeze home as well as adding a wood chopping block and armor work bench behind the home. Willing to to suggestions for improvement.
descriptionHtml: This is a mod for the exterior of Breeze home. It adds light decorations along the front, side and back of the home. This mod also adds more shrubs and flowers around the home. The mod only modifies one cell in Whiterun and should be compatible with most other mods. This Mod does NOT change the inside of the home. This the first mod I am uploading to the nexus and am willing to take suggestions of how to improve, and I am willing to fix any bugs or misplaced objects.Â
author: agent732
